(32, 1, 'update', 'Property', 51, 'Updated property: Komplek Villa Mediteranian Dekat GWK - Ungasan', '{\"old\":{\"id\":51,\"admin_id\":\"1\",\"views\":\"8\",\"property_number\":\"PN251200051\",\"title\":\"KOMPLEK VILLA MEDITERANIAN DEKAT GWK - UNGASAN\",\"slug\":\"komplek-villa-mediteranian-dekat-gwk-ungasan\",\"description\":\"villa bergaya meditteranian ini akan dibangun sebanyak 10 unit di area yang cukup padat\\r\\ndan mudah diakses sehingga sangat cocok disewakan harian. Villa dengan konsep seperti ini\\r\\nbiasanya ramai peminat karena dinilai unik dan mencirikhaskan Bali yang tropis. Villa ini\\r\\ndapat disewakan di harga 2.5 juta - 4 juta permalamnya, tergantung musik. Jika ingin\\r\\nlebih sederhana, villa 3 kamar tidur ini dapat disewakan di harga 350-400 juta per tahun.\",\"property_type\":\"villas\",\"property_status\":\"AVAILABLE\",\"pic_ref_number\":\"PPB12MAE\",\"pic_name\":\"Pemburu Property Bali\",\"pic_email\":\"pemburupropertybali@gmail.com\",\"pic_whatsapp_number\":\"+6281237741674\",\"price\":\"3300000000.00\",\"price_monthly\":null,\"price_yearly\":null,\"price_freehold\":\"3300000000.00\",\"price_leasehold\":null,\"leasehold_period\":null,\"has_monthly\":false,\"has_yearly\":false,\"location_text\":\"Jl Raya Jimbaran - Uluwatu\",\"latitude\":\"-8.82078400\",\"longitude\":\"115.11746900\",\"land_size\":\"155.00\",\"building_size\":\"127.00\",\"dimension\":\"8x19.3\",\"direction\":\"East\",\"year_of_build\":null,\"floor_level\":\"1\",\"view\":\"Residence\",\"style_design\":\"Mediterranean\",\"surrounding\":\"Villa\",\"imb\":\"-\",\"zone\":\"YELLOW\",\"living_room_type\":\"Open\",\"dining_room_type\":\"Open\",\"kitchen_type\":\"Open\",\"bedroom\":\"3\",\"bathroom\":\"3\",\"ensuite_bathroom\":null,\"extra_room\":\"-\",\"storage\":\"1\",\"swimming_pool\":true,\"terrace\":false,\"balcony\":false,\"shower\":false,\"furniture\":\"Unfurnished\",\"electricity_power\":\"5500\",\"ac_count\":null,\"water_source\":\"PDAM\",\"internet\":null,\"parking_type