(168, 2, 'update', 'Property', 81, 'Updated property: 3+1 BR VILLA DENGAN PEMANDANGAN LAUT DI BUKIT BINTANG - UNGASAN', '{\"old\":{\"id\":81,\"admin_id\":\"2\",\"views\":\"2\",\"property_number\":\"PN260100026\",\"title\":\"3+1 VILLA WITH OCEAN VIEW IN BUKIT BINTANG - UNGASAN\",\"slug\":\"31-villa-with-ocean-view-in-bukit-bintang-ungasan\",\"description\":\"This villa is situated in the Bukit Bintang area, an elevated and prestigious part of Ungasan\\r\\nknown for its wide asphalt roads (10 meters) and breathtaking views of the ocean, toll road,\\r\\nairport, and the iconic Garuda Wisnu Kencana (GWK) statue. The neighborhood is home to\\r\\nmany grand and luxurious villas. For this particular villa, the stunning views can be enjoyed\\r\\nfrom the second floor and the rooftop. That\\u2019s why we highly recommend this property to\\r\\nluxury home seekers\\u2014whether you\'re looking for a permanent residence, a retirement home,\\r\\nor a premium investment. Rental-wise, this villa has great income potential, with nightly rates\\r\\nranging from IDR 7\\u201310 million depending on the season, in line with the current market. FYI:\\r\\nThis villa is in the same row as Villa No. 9 and 10.\",\"property_type\":\"villas\",\"property_status\":\"AVAILABLE\",\"pic_ref_number\":null,\"pic_name\":null,\"pic_email\":null,\"pic_whatsapp_number\":null,\"price\":\"8500000000.00\",\"price_monthly\":null,\"price_yearly\":null,\"price_freehold\":\"8500000000.00\",\"price_leasehold\":null,\"leasehold_period\":null,\"has_monthly\":false,\"has_yearly\":false,\"location_text\":\"Ungasan, Bali\",\"latitude\":null,\"longitude\":null,\"land_size\":\"400.00\",\"building_size\":\"412.00\",\"dimension\":\"20m x 20m\",\"direction\":null,\"year_of_build\":null,\"floor_level\":\"2\",\"view\":null,\"style_design\":null,\"surrounding\":null,\"imb\":null,\"zone\":\"YELLOW\",\"living_room_type\":null,\"dining_room_type\":null,\"kitchen_type\":\"Wet & dry\",\"bedroom\":\"4\",\"bathroom\":\"4\",\"ensui