(235, 1, 'update', 'Property', 76, 'Updated property: VILLA TERBESAR DI KOMPLEKS VILLA KOMERSIAL – UNGASAN', '{\"old\":{\"id\":76,\"admin_id\":\"2\",\"views\":\"2\",\"property_number\":\"PN260100021\",\"title\":\"4 BR VILLA TERBESAR DI KOMPLEKS VILLA KOMERSIAL \\u2013 UNGASAN\",\"slug\":\"4-br-the-largest-villa-in-a-commercial-villa-complex-ungasan\",\"description\":\"Villa ini berlokasi di Jalan Mangelak, komplek villa Hideaway Residence Ungasan. Sebuah komplek villa elite yang tertata rapi, well maintenance dan high occupancy 75-88% . Lebar jalan komplek 6 meter. Villa ini terdiri dari 2 lantai. Lantai 1 terdapat main area (living room, kitchen, dining area, service room, kolam berenang, dan carport untuk 2 mobil. Sedangkan lantai 2  terdapat kamar, balkon dan family room. Villa di komplek ini rata-rata di sewakan harian di harga 2 - 3,5 juta untuk 2 kamar tidur. So, kamu bisa sewakan villa 4 kamar ini di harga 3,5-5 juta per malamnya.\",\"property_type\":\"villas\",\"property_status\":\"AVAILABLE\",\"pic_ref_number\":\"PPB12MAE\",\"pic_name\":\"Pemburu Property Bali\",\"pic_email\":\"pemburupropertybali@gmail.com\",\"pic_whatsapp_number\":\"+6281237741674\",\"price\":\"7500000000.00\",\"price_monthly\":null,\"price_yearly\":null,\"price_freehold\":\"7500000000.00\",\"price_leasehold\":null,\"leasehold_period\":null,\"has_monthly\":false,\"has_yearly\":false,\"location_text\":\"Ungasan, Bali\",\"latitude\":\"-8.82885390\",\"longitude\":\"115.15898640\",\"land_size\":\"405.00\",\"building_size\":\"436.00\",\"dimension\":\"18.4m x 22m\",\"direction\":null,\"year_of_build\":null,\"floor_level\":\"2\",\"view\":\"Residence\",\"style_design\":\"Tropical Modern\",\"surrounding\":null,\"imb\":null,\"zone\":\"YELLOW\",\"living_room_type\":\"Close & Open\",\"dining_room_type\":\"Close & Open\",\"kitchen_type\":\"Close & Open\",\"bedroom\":\"4\",\"bathroom\":\"4\",\"ensuite_bathroom\":null,\"extra_room\":\"0\",\"storage\":\"1\",\"swimming_pool\":true,\"terrace\":false,\"balc