(327, 1, 'update', 'Property', 70, 'Updated property: TERBENGKALAI! 5 APARTMENT DENGAN AKSES HUTAN MANGROVE - JIMBARAN', '{\"old\":{\"id\":70,\"admin_id\":\"2\",\"views\":\"4\",\"property_number\":\"PN260100015\",\"title\":\"PENTHOUSE NEAR FROM TAMAN MUMBUL - JIMBARAN\",\"slug\":\"penthouse-near-from-taman-mumbul-jimbaran\",\"description\":\"This building was constructed in 2019 with the initial concept of five large penthouses, one of which\\r\\nis L-shaped and significantly larger than the others. It features a spacious swimming pool area, a\\r\\nrooftop with views of the mangrove forest (3rd floor), and a small garden situated in the center of\\r\\nthe penthouses. However, due to budget constraints, the project\\u2014which is 90% complete (only\\r\\nrooftop finishing remains)\\u2014is now being sold below market price and is still open to\\r\\nnegotiation. The estimated cost to complete and renovate the building is around IDR 500 million.\\r\\nOnce fully renovated and furnished, the expected monthly rental income would be around IDR 12\\u2013\\r\\n15 million, targeting the foreigner market.\",\"property_type\":\"houses\",\"property_status\":\"AVAILABLE\",\"pic_ref_number\":null,\"pic_name\":null,\"pic_email\":null,\"pic_whatsapp_number\":null,\"price\":\"4800000000.00\",\"price_monthly\":null,\"price_yearly\":null,\"price_freehold\":\"4800000000.00\",\"price_leasehold\":null,\"leasehold_period\":null,\"has_monthly\":false,\"has_yearly\":false,\"location_text\":\"Jimbaran, Bali\",\"area\":null,\"latitude\":null,\"longitude\":null,\"land_size\":\"526.00\",\"building_size\":\"660.00\",\"dimension\":\"20m x 26m\",\"direction\":\"East\",\"year_of_build\":\"2019\",\"floor_level\":\"3\",\"view\":null,\"style_design\":null,\"surrounding\":null,\"imb\":null,\"zone\":\"YELLOW\",\"living_room_type\":null,\"dining_room_type\":null,\"kitchen_type\":null,\"bedroom\":\"5\",\"bathroom\":null,\"ensuite_bathroom\":\"5\",\"extra_room\":null,\"storage\":null,\"swimming_pool\":true,\"terrace\":false,\"balcony\":false,\"shower\":false,\"furniture\":null,\"electricity_power\":null,\"ac_count\":null,\"water_source\":null,\"internet\":null,\"parking_type\":null,\"parking_size\":null,\"monthly_cost_included\":null,\"banjar_security\":false,\"cleaning_service\":false,\"pool_maintenance\":false,\"garden_maintenance\":false,\"bin_collection\":false,\"electricity_included\":false,\"internet_included\":false,\"advisor_notes\":\"Nearby locations:\\r\\nJimbaran Immigration Office \\u2013 700 m (3 minutes)\\r\\nCoco Mart \\u2013 750 m (3 minutes)\\r\\nNusa Dua Toll Gate \\u2013 2.9 km (6 minutes)\\r\\nNusa Dua Beach \\u2013 6.3 km (16 minutes)\",\"created_at\":\"2026-01-05T12:56:59.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-01-17T05:43:02.000000Z\",\"is_featured\":false,\"featured_order\":null},\"new\":{\"title\":\"TERBENGKALAI! 5 APARTMENT DENGAN AKSES HUTAN MANGROVE - JIMBARAN\",\"description\":\"Bangunan ini dibangun di tahun 2019 dengan konsep awal sebagai 5 penthouse besar, dimana 1 diantaranya berbentuk later L dan dibuat sangat besar dari yang lain. Memiliki area kolam berenang yang cukup besar, rooftop dengan pemandangan hutan mangrove (lt 3), dan taman kecil di tengah2 penthouse. Namun akibat kehabisan dana, bangunan yg sudah rampung 90% ini (sisa finishing bagian rooftop) terpaksa dijual dengan harga di bawah pasar dan masih terbuka untuk negosiasi. Adapun kisaran dana yang akan dihabiskan untuk merenovasi bangunan ini di kisaran 500 juta. Angka sewa bulanan paling masuk akal jika sudah direnovasi dan full furnish di angka 12-15 juta per bulan dengan segmentasi pasar foreigner. \\r\\n\\r\\nLokasi dekat dengan : \\r\\nKantor Imigrasi JImbaran - 700 m (3 menit) \\r\\nCoco mart - 750 meter (3 menit)\\r\\nPintu Tol Nusa Dua - 2.9 km (6 menit)\\r\\nPantai Nusa Dua - 6.3 km (16 menit)\",\"property_type\":\"apartments\",\"property_status\":\"AVAILABLE\",\"pic_ref_number\":\"PPB12MAE\",\"pic_name\":\"Pemburu Property Bali\",\"pic_email\":\"pemburupropertybali@gmail.